data.summary_suggestion: Test caller permissions on IAP-protected resource
data.description_suggestion: Tests which Identity and Access Management (IAM) permissions the authenticated caller has on an Identity-Aware Proxy protected resource. Accepts a TestIamPermissionsRequest specifying the resource and permissions to check. Returns a TestIamPermissionsResponse containing the subset of requested permissions that the caller possesses. Returns PERMISSION_DENIED error if the resource does not exist or caller lacks IAP permissions. Useful for authorization checks before attempting privileged operations.
